title: Veteran Organizations, Florida, 2003
name: Veteran Organizations, Florida, 2003
description: This dataset contains 2003 Veteran Organizations and Facilities Information for the State of Florida. It is a combination of veteran associations addresses from the Yellow Pages online and the Department of Vetrans Affairs Facility Directory. This dataset contains fields denoting the physical address, and contact information for veteran facilities located in Florida.
